item.title: CVE-2023-46660|2023-10-25T13:45:59.448Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20zanata%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Zanata Plugin 0.6 and earlier uses a non-constant time comparison function when checking whether the provided and expected webhook token hashes are equal, potentially allowing attackers to use statistical methods to obtain a valid webhook token.
